                    "description": "<i>Puliciphora etiamodesta</i> Disney, nom. nov.   <p> <i>Mesopathusa modesta</i> Disney, in Disney &amp; Kistner, 1989: 85.</p>   <p> <i>Puliciphora modesta</i> (Disney). Disney &amp; Darlington, 1998: 169.</p>   <p>The synonymising of <i>Pulicimyia</i> with <i>Puliciphora</i> (see above) and the resulting transfer of species means that <i>Puliciphora modesta</i> (Borgmeier) comb. nov. (see below) creates a homonym with the Afrotropical <i>P. modesta</i> (Disney). The latter is therefore renamed <i>P. etiamodesta.</i></p>",
