                    "description": "<i>Puliciphora edaphomyia</i> Disney, nom. nov.   <p> <i>Edaphomyia nigriventris</i> Borgmeier, 1959: 194.</p>   <p> <i>Coridophora nigriventris</i> (Borgmeier). Disney, 1982: 10.</p>   <p> <i>Puliciphora nigriventris</i> (Borgmeier). Disney, 2002: 77, not Bohart, 1947: 412.</p>   <p>When the genus <i>Coridophora</i> Schmitz was synonymised with <i>Puliciphora</i> (Disney, 2002) this created a homonym with <i>Puliciphora nigriventris</i> Bohart (1947), a synonym of <i>P. pulex</i> Dahl. I therefore rectify this by renaming the species <i>P. edaphomyia,</i> the name of the genus to which this species was originally assigned, but which was subsequently synonymised with <i>Coridophora</i> (Disney, 1982).</p>",
