                    "description": "<p> <b>Key to Indian species of <i>Amitus</i> Haldeman, 1850 (Based on females)</b> </p>   <p>1. Clava 2.5 &times; as long as wide &hellip;&hellip; <b> <i>A. kiefferi</i> Veenakumari and Buhl</b> </p>   <p>- Clava as long as or more than 3.4 &times; as long as wide &hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;...&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; 2</p>  <p>2. Forewing length more than 3.5 &times; width; head 1.78 &times; as wide as high&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;.&hellip;&hellip;...... <b> <i>A. aleurolobi</i> Mani</b> </p>   <p>- Forewing length less than 3 &times; as width; head less than 1.6 &times; as wide as high&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; 3</p>  <p>3. A 1 5.86 &times; as long as wide; POL greater than 2.5 &times; LOL; POL atleast 2.29 &times; OOL&hellip;..............................&hellip; <b> <i>A. sikkimensis</i> Veenakumari and Buhl</b> </p>   <p>- A 1 4.75 &times; as long as wide; POL less than 2.25 &times; LOL; POL only 1.8 &times; OOL&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;... <b> <i>A. vignus</i> sp. n.</b> </p>",
